      "writtenOn": "2021-06-15T17:41:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So I think this is probably the right fix, but it may be exposing a bug in Pdfium. With this patch Adobe Reader works as expected, but with this patch Pdfium does not apply any alpha. Without this patch Adobe Reader applies both alphas, but Pdfium only one of them. As a result, it appears that perhaps Pdfium is not applying the alpha from the graphics state to Pattern?\n\nOn the one hand, probably worth just landing this and then opening an issue against Pdfium. However, it would be nice to fix that first.",
      "revId": "9c8dc02ddb428bd1398efe38e8ff50e1bed0bb66",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
    {
